{"tid":2505836,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：美國亞裔居民自製小冊子應對仇恨暴力","createTime":"2021-04-27T02:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T02:15:31.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"de88f0eeb536f09d494f979bbfd822fcbd7d0aaa","tid":2505836,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:15:31.000Z","msg":"Asian Lives Matter = Chinese Lives Matter<br />\n<br />\n美國近日再發生亞裔人士在街頭遇襲事件，一名61歲男子在紐約被人從後襲擊，倒地後被多次踢頭，送院後情況危殆。<br />\n<br />\n在事發前一天，即上星期四，參議院通過打擊反亞裔仇恨法案，希望在聯邦層面遏止這類罪案。<br />\n<br />\n過去一年多，<strong>美國境內針對亞裔的仇恨罪案大幅上升</strong>，有亞裔人士自製多種語言的小冊子，教導亞裔人士若遇到襲擊應該如何處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587880-20210427.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587880-20210427.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B64oP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=c8aa02e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587880-20210427.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a586ee9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587880-20210427.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}